      "content": "wait im actually really dizzy now and my heart is racing. i tried some juice like u said but it didnt seem to help much. i checked my monitor and the number is actually really high, like 280. if its actually high, wouldnt more insulin be the right thing to do to bring it down? i feel like i need to do something fast.",
